properties.areaDesc: Delaware Bay waters south of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE; Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 10 at 2:55AM EST until January 12 at 3:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...South to southwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30
kt and rough waters expected.

* WHERE...Delaware Bay.

* WHEN...From 6 PM Saturday to 3 PM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM SATURDAY TO 3 PM EST SUNDAY
